pe="text/javascript" src="/lib/js/star/jquery.MetaData.js"></script><script type="text/javascript" src="/lib/js/star/jquery.rating.js"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/lib/css/star/star.css"><script type="text/javascript" src="/lib/js/jquery.ba-hashchange.min.js"></script><style type="text/css">.col960menu { display: none!important; }</style><script type="text/javascript">var globalRate = {}; $.get("/rate.txt",function(resp){ var trresp = resp.split("|");$.each( trresp, function( i,a ){ var ttee = a.split( "," );  if(ttee[0]) { globalRate[ttee[0]] = ttee[1]; } } ) }); </script><script type="text/javascript" src="/lib/js/self-ad.js"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/lib/css/self-ad.css"><style type="text/css">body { background-color: rgb(232,235,237);background-image: url("/upload/201407/2012-04-14-052.jpg");background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: 50% 0%;}.layout a { }</style><script type="text/javascript">var trustr = "19061df5a195e9666169b86b6bb0c3a6"</script><meta id="description_pg" name="description" content=""><meta id="keywords_pg" name="keywords" content=""><title>StandMaster - ZABUDOWA STOISK TARGOWYCH</title></head><body><div class="cookie-alert" style="background:##F2FFE1"><div class="cookie-wrapper"><p>Strona korzysta z plikow cookies w celu realizacji uslug i zgodnie z Polityka Plikow Cookies. Mozesz okreslic warunki przechowywania lub dostepu do plikow cookies w Twojej przegladarce.</p><a class="cookie-close" href="#">Akceptuje, nie pokazuj wiecej</a></div></div><input type="hidden" name="websiteid" id="websiteid" value="126703"><div id="main" class="layout layout_3"><div style="" id="col960" class="column col960"><div style=""><div style="overflow:auto;width: auto; height: auto;"><div class="module module-photo" style="text-align: left;"><div class="photo-wrapp" style="max-width: 100%;"><img src="/upload/201407/SM_logo.jpg" style="height:299px;width:298px;"></div></div></div></div></div><div style="" id="col960menu" class="column col960menu"></div><div style="" id="col310left" class="column col310left"><div class="module module-Header module-header" style=""><h1 style="">O nas</h1></div><div class="module module-text" style=""><div style=""><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">Jestesmy firma dzialajaca w branzy wystawienniczej - zajmujemy sie projektowaniem i zabudowa stoisk targowych oraz doradztwem w tym zakresie. <br><br>Swiadczymy uslugi dla mikro, malych, srednich, duzych przedsiebiorstw oraz dla klientow korporacyjnych z calego swiata.<br></span><br><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">Wystawiennictwo jest rodzajem marketingu bezposredniego - jedna z nabardziej skutecznych form marketingu.</span> <br><br>Dla<span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"> wielu firm jest najistotniejszym elementem strategii marketingowej.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">To, ze znalezli sie Panstwo na naszej stronie, oznacza, iz rowniez dla Panstwa udzial w targach jest droga do rozwoju i ekspansji na rynku krajowym i miedzynarodowym.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><strong><br><span style="color: #464cb8;"><!--StartFragment--><strong style="text-align: center; color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: #3475ba; font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><!--StartFragment--><strong style="color: #1875f7; text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">Proponujemy Panstwu nasze uslugi:</strong></span></strong><br></span></strong></span></p>
<ul><li><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">projektowania i zabudowy stoisk</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">doradztwa z zakresu marketingu wystawienniczego</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">managementu wystawienniczego</span></li>
</ul><div style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #3475ba; font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><!--StartFragment--><strong style="color: #1875f7; text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">PRZED TARGAMI</strong><br></span></strong></div>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">opracowujemy z Panstwem ogolna strategie wystawiennicza</span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">opracowujemy liste targow oraz imprez branzowych i precyzujemy Panstwa cele</span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">opracowujemy plan dzialania</span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">wypelniamy formularze</span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">szkolimy personel</span></div>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #3073ba; font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><strong><!--StartFragment--><strong style="color: #1875f7; text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">NA TARGACH</strong><!--EndFragment--><br></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">koordynujemy zabudowe stoiska</span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">koordynujemy dostawe Panstwa produktow/wyposazenia</span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">koordynujemy dzialania firm zewnetrznych: catering, ekipy sprzatajace, firmy naglosnieniowe<br><br></span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #3073ba; font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><!--StartFragment--><strong style="color: #1875f7; text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">PO TARGACH</strong><br></span></strong></div>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">koordynujemy demontaz stoiska</span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><br>koordynujemy wszelkie dzialania logistyczne (np. wysylke Panstwa produktow/wyposazenia do siedziby Panstwa firmy lub naszego magazynu)</span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">przeprowadzamy ewaluacje projektu wystawienniczego czyli Panstwa udzialu <br>w targach<br></span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">formulujemy zalecenia na nastepne targi</span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"> <br><br><br>Zapraszamy do wspolpracy!</span></div></div></div><div style=""><div style="overflow:auto;width: auto; height: auto;"><div class="module module-photo" style="text-align: left;"><div class="photo-wrapp" style="max-width: 100%;"><img src="/upload/201407/shaking2.JPG" style="height:290px;width:290px;"></div></div></div></div></div><div style="" id="col320" class="column col320"><div class="module module-Header module-header" style=""><h1 style="">Oferta</h1></div><div class="module module-text" style=""><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p><span style="font-family: Courier New;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">Prowadzimy i realizujemy projekty wystawiennicze oferujac Panstwu nasze uslugi:</span><br><br><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><span style="color: #c21bc2;"><strong></strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span><span style="color: #1875f7;"><strong>PROJEKTOWANIE</strong></span></span><strong></strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Courier New;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">projektowanie stoisk w srodowisku 3D</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">projektowanie logo 2D i 3D</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Courier New;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">projektowanie materialow reklamowych</span><br><br><span style="color: #1874f5; font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><strong>ZABUDOWA STOISK TARGOWYCH</strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">zabudowa i wyposazenie stoisk</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Georgia;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">demontaz stoisk</span><br><br><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">W zaleznosci od Panstwa potrzeb oferujemy:<br></span></span><span style="font-family: Courier New;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">zabudowe systemowa typu Octanorm</span> </span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">zabudowe indywidualna - drewno lub drewno+system</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><span style="color: #1a73f0;"><strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">Wychodzac Panstwu na przeciw dopasowujemy typ zabudowy oraz linie projektowa do Panstwa budzetu.</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #1a73f0; font-family: Georgia;"><br></span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">ZARZADZANIE PROJEKTAMI WYSTAWIENNICZYMI - <span style="color: #1d75f0;"><strong>EXHIBIT MANAGEMENT & MARKETING</strong></span></span></p>
<ul><li><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">rejestracja udzialu w targach/wynajmu <span style="color: #f7d70a;"></span>powierzchni wystawienniczej</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">skladanie zamowien uslug targowych: przylaczy elektrycznych, wod.-kan., podwieszen</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">doradztwo w obszarze marketingu wystawienniczego</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">ewaluacja uczestnictwa w targach: raport na zyczenie Klienta</span></li>
</ul><span style="font-family: Georgia;"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"></span></span>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">Nasz zespol bedzie towarzyszyl Panstwu od momentu projektowania, poprzez zabudowe po demontaz Panstwa stoiska.<span style="color: #624cc7;"></span><span style="color: #c92bc9;"></span><span style="color: #b04cb0;"></span></span></p>
<p></p></div></div><div class="module module-slideshow" style=""><div class="slider-wrapper theme-default" style=""><div id="slider455235" class="nivoSlider"> <img src="/upload/201407/zdjecia_1454.JPG" alt="" data-thumb="/upload/201407/zdjecia_1454.JPG"><img src="/upload/201503/YellowGreen.jpg" alt="" data-thumb="/upload/201503/YellowGreen.jpg"><img src="/upload/201503/Monologue.jpg" alt="" data-thumb="/upload/201503/Monologue.jpg"><img src="/upload/201503/Louis_Garneau.jpg" alt="" data-thumb="/upload/201503/Louis_Garneau.jpg"><img src="/upload/201503/Ethicheck2.jpg" alt="" data-thumb="/upload/201503/Ethicheck2.jpg"><img src="/upload/201503/Ethicheck1.jpg" alt="" data-thumb="/upload/201503/Ethicheck1.jpg"><img src="/upload/201503/DVS.jpg" alt="" data-thumb="/upload/201503/DVS.jpg"><img src="/upload/201503/Capsbury_Limted.jpg" alt="" data-thumb="/upload/201503/Capsbury_Limted.jpg"><img src="/upload/201407/2012-04-14-052.jpg" alt="" data-thumb="/upload/201407/2012-04-14-052.jpg"></div></div></div><script type="text/javascript">$(document).ready(function() {$("#slider455235").nivoSlider({effect:'fade',slices:15,boxCols:8,boxRows:8,animSpeed:400,pauseTime:3000,startSlide:0,directionNav:true,controlNav:true,controlNavThumbs:false,pauseOnHover:true,manualAdvance:false});});</script></div><div style="" id="col310right" class="column col310right"><div class="module module-Header module-header" style=""><h1 style=""><span style="display: block">About us & Offer</span></h1></div><div class="module module-text" style=""><div style=""><p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">StandMaster company provides stand construction and design services for companies from all over the world.<br><br></span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">Our aim is to build your success at the trade shows and exhibitions. Your satisfaction gives us the best motivation and incentive to expand our horizons.<br><br></span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">Doing what we love is the biggest secret of our business.<br><br></span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">We manage and implement projects by dealing with:<br><br></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #3974db;"><strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><!--StartFragment--><strong style="color: #1875f7; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">DESIGNING</strong><br></span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">stand designing in a 3D environment</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">2D and 3D logo designing<span style="color: #5158d1;"></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">designing of advertising materials<br><br></span><span style="color: #3875de;"><strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><!--StartFragment--><strong style="color: #1875f7; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">EXHIBITION STANDS CONSTRUCTION </strong><!--EndFragment--><br></span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">stand construction<br>furniture and equipment rental</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">stand dismantle<br><br></span><span style="color: #3773db;"><strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><!--StartFragment--><strong style="color: #1875f7; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">EXHIBIT MANAGEMENT & MARKETING</strong></span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">registration forms</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">exhibition area rental</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">electricity and other services supply orders</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><span style="color: #7197e3;"></span>exhibit marketing consulting<br><br>O</span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">ur team will be with you all the way through, from designing to dismantling the booth, to help your company to get the most from the exhibition and not worry about the details.<br><br>Let's build your success together!<strong></strong></span></p></div></div><div class="module module-Header module-header" style=""><h1 style=""><span style="display: block">Contact</span></h1></div><div class="module module-text" style=""><div style=""><strong><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">StandMaster</span></strong><br><br><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">ul. Strzelecka 21 lok. 3</span><br><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">40-073 Katowice</span><br><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">Poland</span><br><br><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;"><a href="mailto:info@standmaster.pl">info@standmaster.pl</a></span><br><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS;">www.standmaster.pl</span></div></div><div style=""><div style="overflow:auto;width: auto; height: auto;"><div class="module module-photo" style="text-align: left;"><div class="photo-wrapp" style="max-width: 100%;"><img src="/upload/201408/contact.JPG" style="height:195px;width:170px;"></div></div></div></div><div eeemmm="455377" class="module" id="form_762" style=""><div style="width: auto; font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt;"><form enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded" onsubmit="return funcsendformact_form_762();" action="" method="post"><dl class="zend_form"><div class="form-element form-element-text" id="imiinazwiskoWrapper">
